      <h2 class="pb-16 text-3xl font-semibold">Our Approach</h2>
      <div
        class="flex h-full w-full flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-8 lg:flex-row"
      >
        <p class="w-full flex-1 text-3xl lg:w-1/4 xl:text-4xl">
          The Growth <br />
          Catalyst Formula
        </p>
        <div
          class="grid w-full flex-2 grid-cols-1 gap-6 gap-y-12 md:grid-cols-2"
        >
          <div class="md:w-[310px] xl:w-[400px]">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">We Listen First</h3>
            <p>
              Every organization is unique, so we take time to understand your
              needs and tailor solutions that truly fit.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-[310px] xl:w-[400px]">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">We Deliver What Matters</h3>
            <p>
              From real-world tools to fresh ideas, we focus on impact, not just
              ticking boxes.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-[310px] xl:w-[400px]">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">We Walk the Journey with You</h3>
            <p>
              Our team is skilled, passionate, flexible, and committed to seeing
              you succeed.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-[310px] xl:w-[400px]">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">We are committed to excellence</h3>
            <p>
              From planning to execution, we uphold high standards in everything
              we do
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="w-screen space-y-8 p-8 text-xl sm:p-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium">Our Services</h2>
      <div
        class="flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-between space-y-8 lg:flex-row lg:space-y-0 lg:space-x-8"
        id="leader"
      >
        <div class="w-full space-y-4 lg:w-1/2">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-(--primary)">Leadership Development</h3>
          <p>
            We shape leaders and build cohesive teams through immersive,
            results-driven programs.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >01</span
              >
              <p>
                Self-Leadership: Strengthen vision, discipline, and career
                direction.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >02</span
              >
              <p>
                Team Effectiveness: Boost trust, collaboration, and
                communication.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >03</span
              >
              <p>
                Leader Development: Equip leaders to mentor, coach, and build
                succession pipelines.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >04</span
              >
              <p>
                Adventure Learning (Camping): Outdoor challenges that foster
                teamwork and leadership.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            <span class="pr-4 font-semibold text-(--primary)">Outcomes:</span
            >Stronger leadership pipeline, engaged teams, better
            decision-making.
          </p>
        </div>
        <Image
          src={Home1}
          alt="An image of people in an office"
          width="600"
          height="500"
          class="aspect-auto w-full lg:w-1/2"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-between space-y-8 lg:flex-row-reverse lg:space-y-0 lg:space-x-8"
        id="hr"
      >
        <div class="w-full space-y-4 lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-(--primary)">Human Resource Consulting</h3>
          <p>
            We design agile, performance-driven HR frameworks that support
            growth.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >01</span
              >
              <p>Talent Sourcing & Recruitment</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >02</span
              >
              <p>Organization Design & Job Evaluation</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >03</span
              >
              <p>Human Resource Audits</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >04</span
              >
              <p>Talent & Performance Management</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >05</span
              >
              <p>Remuneration & Rewards</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >06</span
              >
              <p>Training solutions & curriculum development</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            <span class="pr-4 font-semibold text-(--primary)">Outcomes:</span
            >Smarter hiring, fit-for-purpose structures, higher retention, and
            sustainable high performance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <Image
          src={Home2}
          alt="An image of people in an office"
          width="600"
          height="500"
          class="aspect-auto w-full lg:w-1/2"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-between space-y-8 lg:flex-row lg:space-y-0 lg:space-x-8"
        id="health"
      >
        <div class="w-full space-y-4 lg:w-1/2">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-(--primary)">Workspace Health and Safety</h3>
          <p>
            We help organizations build a culture of safety, compliance, and
            resilience.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >01</span
              >
              <p>First Aid & Emergency Care</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >02</span
              >
              <p>Fire Safety & Evacuation Training</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >03</span
              >
              <p>Custom Safety Programs</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >04</span
              >
              <p>Health & Safety Audits</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            <span class="pr-4 font-semibold text-(--primary)">Outcomes:</span
            >Reduced workplace incidents, compliance with OSH Act, improved
            morale, business continuity.
          </p>
        </div>
