        <div class="w-full space-y-4 lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-(--primary)">Team Building & Camping</h3>
          <p>
            <span class="font-medium italic"
              >"In every walk with nature one receives far more than he seeks."</span
            >
            — John Muir
          </p>
          <p>
            We create transformative experiences that strengthen collaboration
            and personal growth.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >01</span
