            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >02</span
              >
              <p>
                Life skills training (first aid, conflict resolution, survival
                skills)
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start">
              <span
                class="w-[80px] shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-(--primary)"
                >03</span
              >
              <p>Campfire sessions (storytelling, music, talent sharing)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            <span class="pr-4 font-semibold text-(--primary)">Outcomes:</span
            >Stronger teams, improved communication, lasting memories.
          </p>
        </div>
        <Image
          src={Home4}
          alt="An image of people in an office"
          width="600"
          height="500"
          class="aspect-auto w-full lg:w-1/2"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-6 px-8 sm:px-16" id="team">
      <h2 class="text-3xl">Our Team</h2>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between space-y-6 md:flex-row md:items-start md:space-y-0 md:space-x-12 lg:space-x-24 xl:justify-center xl:space-x-56"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6 sm:w-[500px]"
        >
          <img
            src="/david.jpeg"
            alt="Photo"
            class="aspect-square w-[280px] rounded-full border md:w-[400px]"
          />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">David Kariuki</h3>
          <p>
            Human Resource & Leadership Expert | Certified Executive Coach <br
            />
            With 20+ years of experience in financial services, technology, and education,
            David specializes in organization design, culture transformation, talent
            strategy, and executive coaching. He has worked with leading organizations
            across East Africa, delivering impactful HR and leadership solutions
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6 sm:w-[500px]"
        >
          <img
            src="/namu.jpeg"
            alt="Photo"
            class="aspect-square w-[280px] rounded-full border md:w-[400px]"
          />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">Richard Namu</h3>
