            Occupational Safety & HR Specialist | Certified Fire & Emergency
            Instructor <br />
            Richard brings over a decade of expertise in health & safety training,
            audits, and emergency response. His work spans humanitarian agencies,
            corporates, schools, and media houses across Africa, supporting organizations
            to build resilient and safe workplaces.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section
      class="flex flex-row items-center justify-center px-8 py-8 sm:px-16"
      id="contact"
    >
      <div
        class="w-full rounded-4xl bg-(--primary) p-8 text-white md:p-16 xl:w-4/5"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between space-y-8 md:flex-row md:space-y-0"
        >
          <div class="w-full space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Work with us today</h2>
            <p>We have served a variety of industries including</p>
            <div class="space-y-3 md:pl-8">
              <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start space-x-6">
                <img src="/assets/tick.svg" alt="-" />
                <p>Finance</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start space-x-6">
                <img src="/assets/tick.svg" alt="-" />
                <p>Hospitality</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start space-x-6">
                <img src="/assets/tick.svg" alt="-" />
                <p>Education</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start space-x-6">
                <img src="/assets/tick.svg" alt="-" />
                <p>Corporate sectors</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Text us on Whatsapp : +254 718 168875</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">Text us on Instagram: @FortuneLeadke</p>
          </div>
          <form
            class="flex w-full flex-col space-y-3"
            method="POST"
            action="register.php"
          >
            <div class="w-full space-y-4">
              <label for="email" class="text-xl font-semibold"
                >Enter your email</label
              >
              <input
                type="email"
                name="email"
                placeholder="Enter your best email"
                class="w-full rounded-lg bg-white px-3 py-3 text-black"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-full space-y-4">
                <label for="surname" class="text-xl font-semibold"
                  >Surname</label
                >
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="surname"
                  placeholder="Doe"
                  class="w-full rounded-lg bg-white px-3 py-3 text-black"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="w-full space-y-4">
                <label for="firstname" class="text-xl font-semibold"
                  >Firstname</label
                >
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="firstname"
                  placeholder="John"
                  class="w-full rounded-lg bg-white px-3 py-3 text-black"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full space-y-4">
              <label for="phone" class="text-xl font-semibold"
                >Your phone number</label
              >
              <input
                type="phone"
                name="phone"
                placeholder="+254 712345678"
                class="w-full rounded-lg bg-white px-3 py-3 text-black"
              />
            </div>
            <button
              class="my-3 w-full rounded-lg bg-white px-6 py-4 font-bold text-(--primary)"
            >
              Submit
            </button>
          </form>
